## Path aliases (typical; see app `tsconfig`)

- `@components/*` тЖТ `client/components/*`
- `@layouts/*` тЖТ `client/layouts/*`
- `@pages/*` тЖТ `client/pages/*`
- `@content/*` тЖТ `content/*`
- `@scripts/*`, `@styles/*`, `@images/*` тАФ Under `client/assets/` as configured
- `@src/*` тЖТ `client/*`
- `@server/*` тЖТ server or configured server root
- `~/*` тЖТ project root

